WEBVTT

00:02.597 --> 00:06.633
McDonald's CEO has resigned after almost 25 years at the fast-food chain...

00:06.841 --> 00:09.173
...and will be replaced by its chief brand officer.

00:09.661 --> 00:11.479
According to a press release from the company,...

00:11.814 --> 00:13.887
...Don Thompson will step down from his position...

00:13.993 --> 00:17.267
...at the top of the iconic restaurant business effective March 1st.

00:17.623 --> 00:21.701
He will be replaced by Steve Easterbrook, who will also serve as president of McDonald's...

00:21.853 --> 00:23.685
...and sit on the company's board of directors.

00:24.177 --> 00:27.749
McDonald's stock was trading about 2% higher in after-hours trading.

00:28.251 --> 00:31.018
Thompson had been under pressure to rehab the restaurant's business,...

00:31.201 --> 00:32.299
...which struggled recently.

00:32.600 --> 00:38.175
In 2014, the company posted its first decline in global same-store sales since 2002.

